{"tid":767513,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［台積電］生産工具遭電腦病毒感染 生産線被迫暫停運作","createTime":"2018-08-04T14:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T00:01:03.000Z","uid":1714,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"14f19e8a4aa58ac4149d779bb6bdb4dd3b4a7f87","tid":767513,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-d-F8HLh3q18/W2W68Z7yv_I/AAAAAAABv0o/OIzEQSrddfU0LhrJlvZkljyJutdCikD-wCLcBGAs/s1600/tsmcvirus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-d-F8HLh3q18%2FW2W68Z7yv_I%2FAAAAAAABv0o%2FOIzEQSrddfU0LhrJlvZkljyJutdCikD-wCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Ftsmcvirus.png&h=56ba74bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thealpha.app/2018/08/tsmcvirus.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thealpha.app%2F2018%2F08%2Ftsmcvirus.html%3Fm%3D1&d=lfJ9k9yE%2BQUrFpGwk%2Frh0J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=97fa281a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thealpha.app/2018/08/tsmcvirus.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\nApple主要晶片製造商台積電嘅晶片生産工具今日被電腦病毒感染，導至佢哋嘅生産線要暫停運作。彭博社引述台積電指，今次嘅事故並唔係由黑客導致，但暫時未知事故原因。廠商嘅生産線已經部份恢復返運作，有啲會遲少少先開返。<br />\n<br />\n呢次係台積電首次發生呢類型直接影響生産線嘅意外，佢哋亦稱每間工廠嘅感染程度都唔同，將會喺嚟緊幾日公佈更詳細嘅資料。"},{"pid":"40aa1aed335677a4c2a2e5f978d20704c7ef09c5","tid":767513,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"有鬼！"},{"pid":"a425a70741d82fbaa0e3edfa287daf3f881c6149","tid":767513,"uid":161990,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未看先猜係贏國"},{"pid":"b4c956e8e82aff9ef1c84b9d5a98190bbd57ccec","tid":767513,"uid":44454,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"沒事，解決不到生產芯片，解決生產芯片的人就可以了"},{"pid":"b9073a2829a29379b598bbf974fbfc02ce4710cc","tid":767513,"uid":52946,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T1